# OT Sentinel — Sensitive MQTT Topics CDB List
# ===========================================
# Format: TOPIC_PATTERN:Description
#
# Used by rule 200032 (OT-SENTINEL-MQTT-003) to detect retained messages
# on sensitive topics. Retained messages are stored by the broker and
# delivered to every new subscriber — poisoning a retained message on a
# critical topic affects all future clients.
#
# Deployment: Copy to /var/ossec/etc/lists/ and add to ossec.conf:
#   <list>etc/lists/sensitive_mqtt_topics</list>

# Critical Control Topics
control/pump/+/cmd:Pump_Control_Commands
control/valve/+/cmd:Valve_Control_Commands
control/breaker/+/cmd:Breaker_Control_Commands
alarm/critical/#:Critical_Alarms
setpoint/#:Setpoint_Changes

